Definition: deep and harsh sounding as if from shouting or illness or emotion
Example: gruff voices; the dog's gruff barking; hoarse cries; makes all the instruments sound powerful but husky- Virgil Thomson
Synonyms: noun, attribute, gruffness, hoarse, hoarseness, husky, huskiness, deep, and, harsh, sounding, as, if, from, shouting, or, illness, emotion, voices, the, dog, s, barking, cries, makes, all, instruments, sound, powerful, but, -, Virgil, Thomson
Category: adj.all
